# Omnifact n8n Community Node

- This package is `n8n-nodes-omnifact`, an n8n community node for the Omnifact API.
- Prefer existing repository patterns over new abstractions.
- Use TypeScript strict-mode friendly code and keep edits scoped to the requested behavior.
- Do not add external runtime dependencies for verified node behavior.
- Do not use env vars or filesystem access inside node runtime code.
- Use Prettier defaults from `.prettierrc.js`: tabs, single quotes, trailing commas, LF, and 100-character print width.
- Verify substantive changes with `npm run lint` and `npm run build` when practical.

## Expected Structure

- Credentials live in `credentials/OmnifactApi.credentials.ts`.
- The main node class is `Omnifact` in `nodes/Omnifact/Omnifact.node.ts`.
- Resource operations live under `nodes/Omnifact/resources/<resourceName>/`.
- Shared descriptions and transport helpers live under `nodes/Omnifact/shared/`.
- Icons exist as light/dark SVG pairs in `nodes/Omnifact/` and `icons/`.
